data.title: OxiClean Spray Stain Remover Begins to Work on Contact
data.description:
Need to remove tough stains fast? OxiClean Laundry Stain Remover Spray starts working on contact to make tough stains disappear!

The power of oxygen can remove even the toughest stains, including red wine stains, chocolate stains and even blueberry stains!

OxiClean works better than the leading stain remover sprays! Use OxiClean pre-treater spray to make tough stains disappear fast!

For an extra boost, adding a scoop of OxiClean Versatile Stain Remover to your laundry boosts your detergent's stain-fighting power, keeps your whites whiter and colors from fading!
